arStrings.szText: "Cori sent me. He's worried about you."

Ah, you spoke to Cori? Hmph, can't believe he even remembers he has a family. I had to throw the loafer out of the house months ago because he refused to work. Didn't hear a peep from him 'til now. Heâ€™s better off in Cerrigar, and we are too.
